scene.message:
Doctor: Now then, what'll{nl}
it be?{nl}
{ctl0e:17}{ret}

Doctor: It'll cost 1500 yen.{nl}
Is that all right?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Doctor: A shame, but I can't{nl}
treat you with no money...{nl}
Come back with the fee.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Skimp on treatment{nl}
now, and I hope it won't{nl}
come back to bite you.{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: I'm a busy man. If{nl}
you've no business here,{nl}
off you go.{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: Don't go letting Maki{nl}
get hurt. She's the town's{nl}
idol, after all.{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: Oh, you're from the{nl}
same school as Maki Sonomura.{waitkey}{clearbox}Huh? You're friends with her?!{nl}
Friends with the town idol —{nl}
how envious I am~!!{waitkey}Get me an autograph sometime!!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: An idol? That's not{nl}
true at all... Everyone's{nl}
just been made to think so...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:88} For Sonomura,{nl}
who knows everything, those{nl}
words must sting

 injuries!{nl}
Give me a cure for my clever{nl}
noggin instead.{waitkey}{ret}
